Motion Sensing Toolkit 
for tracking motion vectors in space

Copyright (c) 2011 invertednothing.
http://invertednothing.com/


Based on the Openframeworks C++ Framework (http://openframeworks.cc/), 
OpenCV Computer Vision Framework (http://opencv.willowgarage.com/),
ofxCv OpenCV Openframeworks Wrapper (https://github.com/kylemcdonald/ofxCv)

loosely resampling the structure of openTSPS (https://github.com/labatrockwell/openTSPS)


